## Input / Output Redirection

```
>  overwrite
>> append
<  input
|  pipe
```

Examples:

```
echo "hello" > file.txt
echo "world" >> file.txt
cat < file.txt
```

Pipe:

```
cat file.txt | grep hello
```

### Practice (redirection)

1.

```
