## Loops

### for loop

```
for i in 1 2 3 4 5
do
    echo $i
done
```

### while loop

```
i=1
while [ $i -le 5 ]
do
    echo $i
    ((i++))
done
```

### Practice (loops)

1.

```
for i in 1 2 3 4 5
do
    echo $i
done
```

2.

```
for i in {1..10}
do
    echo $i
done
```

3.

```
i=1
while [ $i -le 10 ]
do
    echo $i
    ((i++))
done
```

4.

```
for file in *.txt
do
    echo $file
done
```

